OL,7,FAlex Salmond was a colourful
OL,8,Fpolitician who never shied away from
OL,9,Fcontroversy over his long and storied
OL,10,Fcareer in Scottish politics.
OL,12,FFrom falling out with former allies at
OL,13,Fthe SNP to forming his own political
OL,14,Fparty, his personality loomed large
OL,15,Fover the country's political landscape.
OL,17,FHere are some of the more
OL,18,Fcontroversial moments in the Alba
OL,19,Fleader's career:
