OL,7,FIn 2018, the Scottish government set
OL,8,Fup a new procedure for investigating
OL,9,Fcomplaints against ministers and
OL,10,Fformer ministers.
OL,12,FTwo female staff made internal
OL,13,Fcomplaints against Mr Salmond.
OL,15,FHowever, he immediately complained
OL,16,Fthat the process was unfair and
OL,17,Flaunched a judicial review in the
OL,18,Fcourts.
