OL,7,FThe Court of Session ruled the
OL,8,FScottish Government's investigation
OL,9,Finto the claims was "tainted with
OL,10,Fapparent bias" by the investigating
OL,11,Fofficer's prior contact with the
OL,12,Fcomplainants, with Mr Salmond
OL,13,Freceiving more than #500,000 in
OL,14,Fdamages.
OL,16,FThis would ultimately lead to a
OL,17,Fparliamentary inquiry, however, Mr
OL,18,FSalmond's troubles were not over.
