OL,7,FMr Salmond was charged with a litany
OL,8,Fof sexual offences against nine women
OL,9,Fin January 2019.
OL,11,FThe trial, which took place in March
OL,12,Fthe following year, lasted 11 days.
OL,14,FMr Salmond denied all the charges and
OL,15,Fgiving evidence claimed some were
OL,16,F"deliberate fabrications for a
OL,17,Fpolitical purpose"
