OL,7,FDuring a procedural hearing of the
OL,8,Fcase, reporting of which was banned
OL,9,Funtil the end of the trial, Mr
OL,10,FSalmond's defence team claimed the
OL,11,FScottish Government and those working
OL,12,Fthere turned to the criminal process
OL,13,Fto try to "discredit" him after he won
OL,14,Fa civil case into how the
OL,15,Fadministration handled sexual
OL,16,Fharassment complaints against him.
OL,18,FJudge Lady Dorrian rejected an
OL,19,Fapplication for this evidence to be
OL,20,Fled at the trial, saying the judicial
OL,21,Freview was "wholly irrelevant".
