OL,7,F` End of relationship with SNP and
OL,8,Flaunch of Alba party
OL,10,FAs a result of his harassment and
OL,11,Fsexual assault cases, Mr Salmond's
OL,12,Frelationship with his former
OL,13,Fcolleagues at the SNP soured.
OL,15,FA Holyrood inquiry into the handling
OL,16,Fof complaints against Mr Salmond
OL,17,Fcalled both the former first minister
OL,18,Fand Ms Sturgeon ` who was still
OL,19,Fserving in the role at that point ` to
OL,20,Ftestify in two marathon sessions.
