OL,7,FMr Salmond accused those at the
OL,8,Fhighest echelons of the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment of a plot against him,
OL,10,Fsomething Ms Sturgeon called "absurd".
OL,12,FIn 2021, Mr Salmond launched the Alba
OL,13,FParty, which has spent much of its
OL,14,Fexistence criticising the SNP ` headed
OL,15,Fthen by Ms Sturgeon and subsequently
OL,16,Fby two of her key allies in Humza
OL,17,FYousaf and John Swinney.
OL,19,FHowever, the party has failed to make
OL,20,Fa sizeable impact on Scottish politics.
