OL,12,F` Friendship and falling out with
OL,13,FDonald Trump
OL,15,FMr Salmond developed an unlikely
OL,16,Ffriendship with the former US
OL,17,Fpresident after he helped back the
OL,18,Fdevelopment of Mr Trump's Menie golf
OL,19,Fcourse in Aberdeenshire in 2007.
