OL,7,FHowever, the pair fell out in 2012
OL,8,Fover plans to place wind turbines off
OL,9,Fthe coast of the estate.
OL,11,FAfter the real estate mogul's attempt
OL,12,Fto block the construction of the wind
OL,13,Ffarm was shot down by the Supreme
OL,14,FCourt, Mr Salmond branded his former
OL,15,Ffriend "three times a loser".
OL,17,FSpeaking about their relationship
OL,18,Flater in 2018, he said he regretted
OL,19,Fbefriending Mr Trump.
